{"id": 549, "genre": 1001, "title": "为什么说我是个羞涩内敛的人？", "description": "蛇精病只是想亲近这世界的伪装。", "record_count": 9009, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071944315QCG4ZFIRqhgALtH.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-08T11:31:50Z", "options": [{"id": 15616, "content": "不熟悉时会让人觉得你好冷，熟悉了就像个二逼。对女生感电却不知道怎么放电，还害怕说错话。说错后就会很介怀，但是对方却不会在意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236201}, {"id": 16640, "content": "噢 只是和你们不熟而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214264}, {"id": 15617, "content": "因为无言(无颜)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236222}, {"id": 20226, "content": "看情况", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269363}, {"id": 15363, "content": "处女座 A 型血", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151325}, {"id": 15619, "content": "喜欢一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208838}, {"id": 15875, "content": "觉得自己更高端大气上档次", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234356}, {"id": 22531, "content": "跟陌生人讲话容易脸红 … 高原红", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237122}, {"id": 15364, "content": "并不想合他们的群", "image": null, "praise_count": 914, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234148}, {"id": 15620, "content": "我也想跟大家笑哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197195}, {"id": 22788, "content": "不熟?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191300}, {"id": 15621, "content": "并不是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78309}, {"id": 15877, "content": "并不是寡言，只是内心戏永远多于说出口的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218623}, {"id": 17669, "content": "问一句答一句，问两句答一句，不问天黑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255032}, {"id": 15367, "content": "摩羯座", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233452}, {"id": 15879, "content": "跟陌生人不知道要聊什么....怕尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236650}, {"id": 15368, "content": "宅", "image": null, "praise_count": 432, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190208}, {"id": 17161, "content": "因为你是一个闷骚型", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252074}, {"id": 15370, "content": "水瓶座表面的疯狂只为了掩盖内心的寂寞…", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224007}, {"id": 17162, "content": "因为我爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252079}, {"id": 15627, "content": "双鱼座o型血", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236383}, {"id": 44043, "content": "装逼……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440413}, {"id": 15372, "content": "从来都不是自来熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 956, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209723}, {"id": 16141, "content": "觉得他们好无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241505}, {"id": 15374, "content": "气场不合", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164080}, {"id": 15375, "content": "讨厌人类", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233957}, {"id": 17423, "content": "就是不喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253381}, {"id": 15376, "content": "尴尬症发作太频繁\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 537, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 19216, "content": "不好意思和男孩子主动说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263163}, {"id": 15377, "content": "买东西会换不同家买，老在一家会尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 176, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231877}, {"id": 15633, "content": "身边有人大吵大闹，头会痛", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211141SJOyoq8wBHnjGukx.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235433}, {"id": 15378, "content": "我这样的稍稍透露一下内心就会被人认为是很黄很暴力的变态", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223367}, {"id": 15379, "content": "射手座内心火热", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141365}, {"id": 15891, "content": "希望可以吸引男生 然并卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227722}, {"id": 15380, "content": "逃不过的社交散场的那一刻，我的天空，星星都亮了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138266}, {"id": 15381, "content": "不会聊天，或者和别人聊不到一块", "image": null, "praise_count": 544, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234209}, {"id": 16149, "content": "偶尔出去用", "image": "img/option/option/201606052111347BfRg1mPTGjSNx5c.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241611}, {"id": 15382, "content": "不羞涩不内敛的罗永浩是个反面。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211140EF36u2zsmQAJRyg8.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 15638, "content": "能打字绝不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236479}, {"id": 16150, "content": "大家都在说的废话不多说 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241606}, {"id": 15383, "content": "两个字：不熟", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193325bYPcU3RdtxNL6nFq.jpg", "praise_count": 454, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 15639, "content": "不想交谈太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159059}, {"id": 16151, "content": "做好自己的事就行了 ", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211255T2suKGM3eAPgWRHJ.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241611}, {"id": 16665, "content": "觉得说这也不是那也不是，索性不说，听……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234048}, {"id": 15386, "content": "错 是内敛 但不羞涩。。。许多“关我屁事？” 我用微笑来表达。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 15257}, {"id": 15387, "content": "硬不起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234263}, {"id": 16411, "content": "因为没话题，没文化，没口才，然后只能说自己……内敛内涵内心强大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245288}, {"id": 15644, "content": "只是想自己一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199873}, {"id": 16156, "content": "巨蟹座", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241395}, {"id": 15389, "content": "对于发言，更喜欢聆听", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233311}]}